In the event that after Phase 1, the Parties conclude that it would not be economically viable to enter the US market as envisaged, this Agreement shall terminate forthwith and the Parties shall use reasonable efforts to assess whether to proceed with an alternative agreement or not.

If the Agreement is terminated, the Parties shall endeavour to ensure that assets contributed by each Party shall, so far as possible, be transferred back to that Party.
